				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$y_{t}^{U}$\end{document} as shown in Fig.Â 2. Thus, the uplink UE-BS channel can be estimated during phase I. Simultaneously, the BS uses receive antenna array to transmit the energy signals to all the sensors. The signal received by sensor node can be expressed as yrS\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
